Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:28.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:30.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:35.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:38.02,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:47.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}狂った時計　刻む命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:51.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}こぼれてく記憶の砂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:55.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}芽生えた想いまで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:22:00.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}ねえ　こんなに呆気なく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:07.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消えてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:09.01,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I wish I was there
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:11.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Oh,please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:13.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:17.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度となにも失くさぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:24.44,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}私を忘れて　始めて　Restart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.53,0:22:26.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}No,don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:28.74,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:33.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君を砕くこの悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.75,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}いつか終わりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:42.38,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For now I'll see you off
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:45.80,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:47.84,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:48.97,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}二度と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.22,0:22:53.39,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:55.52,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:22:56.81,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}君と
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.05,0:21:28.22,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:30.43,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的触碰  我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:35.98,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不  请不要对生命无爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.10,0:21:38.02,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}尽管这绝望  不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:47.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}失准的时钟  记录着生命
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.78,0:21:51.62,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}散落满地的记忆之砂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.70,0:21:55.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}以及萌生的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:22:00.46,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你看  却是那么轻易
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:07.76,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}消失殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:09.01,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我希望能与你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.05,0:22:11.05,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:13.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}你的触碰  我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.31,0:22:17.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}为了不再失去曾经拥有的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:24.44,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让我忘却自己的过去  重新开始旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.53,0:22:26.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不  请不要对生命无爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.82,0:22:28.74,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}尽管这绝望  不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.95,0:22:33.16,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}愿那让你苦不堪言的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.75,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}会迎来完结的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.79,0:22:42.38,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}而我却要目送你离开
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:45.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.88,0:22:47.84,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:48.97,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}再一次的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.22,0:22:53.39,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.60,0:22:55.52,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:22:56.81,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}与你携手迈进
